’Ł@c8bb431f096507be1cd0bdac819ac1486acbfc0b24bbefdf2efa9fb467acd831ŁėTitle: title: math arcsin
Path: Examples
Content:
Get the arcsine of 1
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 1 | math arcsin
1.5707963267948966

```
Get the arcsine of 1 in degrees
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 1 | math arcsin --degrees
90.0

```
